---
import Button from "@core/ui/Button.astro"
import { getWhatsappLink } from "src/utils/whatsapp"
---

<section class="relative h-[900px] md:h-[800px] lg:h-[620px] xl:h-[800px] overflow-hidden">
	<div id="parallax-bg" class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[#3c6da9] -z-20"></div>
	<div
		id="building-image"
		class="absolute right-0 top-[520px] md:top-[420px] w-full h-[500px] lg:top-0 lg:h-full -z-10 lg:w-1/2"
	>
	</div>

	<!-- Floating decorative elements -->
	<div class="floating-element left-10 top-1/4 opacity-20">
		<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-dark-orange"></div>
	</div>

	<div class="container h-screen pt-32 md:h-full lg:pt-0">
		<div class="relative h-full lg:flex items-center justify-start text-left px-3">
			<div class="max-w-xl xl:max-w-2xl text-white md:ml-12 hero-text-container">
				<h1 class="text-[40px] md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl font-medium mb-6 leading-11 md:leading-13 xl:leading-16">
					Encuentra tu <span class="text-dark-orange font-black">inmueble ideal</span> con Eiich Inmobiliaria
				</h1>
				<p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-10 opacity-90 max-w-[480px] xl:max-w-xl">
					En Eiich Inmobiliaria, te damos la bienvenida a un espacio donde tus sueños y proyectos toman forma.
					Nos especializamos en la compra y venta de departamentos, terrenos, locales comerciales y más,
					ofreciendo un servicio personalizado, confiable y transparente.
				</p>

				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-start">
					<Button href="#featured" variant="primary" icon="fas fa-search" size="md">Buscar propiedades</Button
					>
					<Button href={getWhatsappLink()} target="_blank" variant="outline" icon="fas fa-phone" size="md"
						>Contactar asesor</Button
					>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	#parallax-bg {
		background-image: url("/images/fondo.webp");
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
	}

	#building-image {
		background-image: url("/images/edificio.webp");
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		transform: perspective(10px) rotateX(0deg);
		transform-origin: right center;
		will-change: transform;
		opacity: 0.8;
		clip-path: polygon(20% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
	}

	.hero-text-container {
		transform: translateY(0);
	}

	.floating-element {
		position: absolute;
		animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
	}

	@keyframes float {
		0% {
			transform: translateY(0px);
		}
		50% {
			transform: translateY(-20px);
		}
		100% {
			transform: translateY(0px);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		#building-image {
			clip-path: none;
		}

